sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ClientApp
    participant EncryptionService
    participant Server

    User->>ClientApp: Send message
    ClientApp->>EncryptionService: Encrypt message
    EncryptionService-->>ClientApp: Return encrypted message
    ClientApp->>Server: Send encrypted message
    Server->>EncryptionService: Decrypt message
    EncryptionService-->>Server: Return decrypted message
    Server->>User: Deliver decrypted message